he Sea of Grass (film)|The Sea of Grass]]''\n| Lutie Cameron\n| Western drama\n| [[Elia Kazan]]\n|-\n| 1947\n| ''[[Song of Love (1947 film)|Song of Love]]''\n| [[Clara Wieck Schumann]]\n| Period drama\n| [[Clarence Brown]]\n|-\n| 1948\n| '' [[State of the Union (film)|State of the Union]]''\n| Mary Matthews\n| Drama\n| [[Frank Capra]]\n|-\n| 1949\n| ''[[Adam's Rib]]''\n| Amanda Bonner\n| Comedy\n| George Cukor\n|-\n| 1951\n| ''[[The African Queen (film)|The African Queen]]''\n| Rose Sayer\n| Adventure\n| [[John Huston]]\n|-\n| 1952\n| ''[[Pat and Mike]]''\n| Patricia \"Pat\" Pemberton\n| Comedy\n| George Cukor\n|-\n| 1955\n| '' [[Summertime (1955 film)|Summertime]]''\n| Jane Hudson\n| Romance\n| [[David Lean]]\n|-\n| 1956\n| '' [[The Rainmaker (1956 film)|The Rainmaker]]''\n| Lizzie Curry\n| Drama\n| [[Joseph Anthony]]\n|-\n| 1956\n| ''[[The Iron Petticoat]]''\n| Vinka Kovelenko\n| Comedy\n| [[Ralph Thomas]]\n|-\n| 1957\n| ''[[Desk Set]]''\n| Bunny Watson\n| Comedy\n| [[Walter Lang]]\n|-\n| 1959\n| '' [[Suddenly, Last Summer (film)|Suddenly, Last Summer]]''\n| Violet Venable\n| Drama\n| [[Joseph L. Mankiewicz]]\n|-\n| 1962\n| ''[[Long Day's Journey into Night (1962 film)|Long Day's Journey into Night]]''\n| Mary Tyrone\n| Period drama\n| [[Sidney Lumet]]\n|-\n| 1967\n| ''[[Guess Who's Coming to Dinner]]''\n| Christina Drayton\n| Comedy drama\n| [[Stanley Kramer]]\n|-\n| 1968\n| '' [[The Lion in Winter (1968 film)|The Lion in Winter]]''\n| [[Eleanor of Aquitaine]]\n| Period drama\n| [[Anthony Harvey]]\n|-\n| 1969\n| '' [[The Madwoman of Chaillot (film)|The Madwoman of Chaillot]]''\n| Aurelia, The Madwoman of Chaillot\n| Comedy drama\n| [[Bryan Forbes]]\n|-\n| 1971\n| ''[[The Trojan Women (film)|The Trojan Women]]''\n| [[Hecuba]]\n| Period drama\n| [[Michael Cacoyannis]]\n|-\n| 1973\n| '' [[A Delicate Balance (film)|A Delicate Balance]]''\n| Agnes\n| Drama\n| [[Tony Richardson]]\n|-\n| 1975\n| ''[[Rooster Cogburn (film)|Rooster Cogburn]]''\n| Eula Goodnight\n| Western\n| [[Stuart Millar]]\n|-\n| 1978\n| '' [[Olly Olly Oxen Free (film)|Olly Olly Oxen Free]]''\n| Miss Pudd\n| Adventure\n| [[Richard A. Colla]]\n|-\n| 1981\n| ''[[On Golden Pond (1981 film)|On Golden Pond]]''\n| Ethel Thayer\n| Drama\n| [[Mark Rydell]]\n|-\n| 1985\n| ''[[Grace Quigley]]''\n| Grace Quigley\n| Comedy\n| Anthony Harvey\n|-\n| 1994\n| '' [[Love Affair (1994 film)|Love Affair]]''\n| Ginny\n| Romantic drama\n| [[Glenn Gordon Caron]]\n|}\n\n===Television films===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n! Director\n|-\n| 1973\n| ''[[The Glass Menagerie (1973 film)|The Glass Menagerie]]''\n| Amanda Wingfield\n| Drama\n| Anthony Harvey\n|-\n| 1975\n| ''[[Love Among the Ruins (film)|Love Among the Ruins]]''\n| Jessica Medlicott\n| Period comedy\n| George Cukor\n|-\n| 1979\n| ''[[The Corn Is Green (1979 film)|The Corn Is Green]]''\n| Lily Moffat\n| Period drama\n| George Cukor\n|-\n| 1986\n| ''[[Mrs. Delafield Wants to Marry]]''\n| Margaret Delafield\n| Romantic comedy\n| [[George Schaefer (director)|George Schaefer]]\n|-\n| 1988\n| ''[[Laura Lansing Slept Here]]''\n| Laura Lansing\n| Comedy\n| George Schaefer\n|-\n| 1992\n| ''[[The Man Upstairs (1992 film)|The Man Upstairs]]''\n| Victoria Brown\n| Comedy drama\n| George Schaefer\n|-\n| 1994\n| ''[[This Can't Be Love (film)|This Can't Be Love]]''\n| Marion Bennett\n| Romantic comedy\n| Anthony Harvey\n|-\n| 1994\n| ''[[One Christmas]]''\n| Cornelia Beaumont\n| Drama\n| [[Tony Bill]]\n|}\n\n===Short subjects===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n! Director\n|-\n| 1941\n| ''Women in Defense''\n| Narrator\n| Documentary\n| \n|-\n| 1946\n| ''American Creed''\n| Narrator\n| Documentary\n| [[Robert Stevenson (director)|Robert Stevenson]]\n|-\n|}\n\n===Box Office Ranking===\n\n{{See also|Top Ten Money Making Stars Poll}}\n\n*1934 - 11th\n*1935 - 23rd\n*1968 - 18th\n*1969 - 9th\n*1970 - 20th\n*1982 - 12th\n\n==Theatre==\n[[File:Katharine Hepburn Rosalind As You Like It 1951.jpg