e web | url=https://www.digisport.ro/fotbal/liga-1/dinamo-jucase-doar-10-meciuri-oficiale-cand-a-batut-o-pe-steaua-in-primul-derby-98962 | title=Dinamo jucase doar 10 meciuri oficiale c\u00e2nd a b\u0103tut-o pe Steaua, \u00een primul derby| publisher=Digisport.ro| language=Romanian |trans-title=Dinamo had only played 10 official matches when they won against Steaua in the first derby| date=28 February 2014| accessdate=28 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.labtof.ro/romania/1948-1949/liga1/11/steaua-bucuresti-1-vs-dinamo-bucuresti-2-1830/|title= Steaua vs Dinamo Liga1 1948\u20131949|publisher=Labtof|accessdate=28 March 2020}}</ref> After ending his playing career, \u0218iclovan first worked at [[Romanian Football Federation|FRF]], later he was a rector at the [[National University of Physical Education and Sport]] from [[Bucharest]] and he also became a [[writer]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.prosport.ro/fotbal-intern/dispare-inca-un-club-de-traditie-din-romania-isi-inchide-portile-dupa-un-secol-de-fotbal-13374310|title=Dispare \u00eenc\u0103 un club de tradi\u021bie din Rom\u00e2nia. \u00ce\u0219i \u00eenchide por\u021bile dup\u0103 un secol de fotbal|publisher=Prosport.ro|language=Romanian |trans-title=Another club of tradition from in Romania disappears. It closes its doors after a century of football |date= 9 October 2014|accessdate= 28 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sportarad.ro/2013/08/24/gloria-arad-implineste-astazi-100-de-ani-crimpeie-dintr-un-secol/|title=Gloria Arad \u00eempline\u0219te ast\u0103zi 100 de ani. Cr\u00eempeie dintr-un secol|publisher=Sportarad.ro|language=Romanian |trans-title=Gloria Arad turns 100 today. Memories from a century |date=24 August 2013|accessdate= 28 March 2020}}</ref><ref name=targul>{{cite web|url=https://www.targulcartii.ro/ion-siclovan|title=Carti Ion Siclovan|publisher=Targulcartii.ro|language=Romanian |trans-title=Books Ion Siclovan |accessdate= 28 March 2020}}</ref><ref name=librarie>{{cite web|url=https://www.librarie.net/p/127636/teoria-educatiei-fizice-si-sportului|title=Teoria educatiei fizice si sportului|publisher=Librarie.ro|language=Romanian |trans-title=The theory of physical education and sportvan |accessdate= 28 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n==International career==\nIon \u0218iclovan played four games at international level for [[Romania national football team|Romania]], including a 3\u20132 victory against [[Bulgaria national football team|Bulgaria]] at the [[1947 Balkan Cup]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://eu-football.info/_player.php?id=19199|title=Ion \u0218iclovan |publisher=European Football|accessdate=28 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://eu-football.info/_match.php?id=6458|title=Bulgaria \u2013 Romania 2:3|publisher=European Football|accessdate=28 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Writing==\nHe wrote two volumes, both of them being about sport:<ref name=targul/><ref name=librarie/>\n* Teoria antrenamentului sportiv ''(The sports training theory)'' (1977)\n* Teoria educatiei fizice si sportului ''(The theory of physical education and sport)'' (1979)\n\n==Notes==\n{{reflist|group=lower-alpha}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n*[http://www.labtof.ro/profil/ion-siclovan-1461/ Ion \u0218iclovan] at Labtof.ro\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:\u0218iclovan, Ion}}\n[[Category:1921 births]]\n[[Category:1985 deaths]]\n[[Category:Romanian footballers]]\n[[Category:Romania international footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football midfielders]]\n[[Category:Liga I players]]\n[[Category:Liga II players]]\n[[Category:Carmen Bucure\u015fti players]]\n[[Category:FC Dinamo Bucure\u0219ti players]]\n[[Category:Romanian writers]]\n[[Category:20th-century Romanian writers]]\n[[Category:Romanian male writers]]\n[[Category:20th-century Romanian male writers]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Arad, Romania]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Romanian footballer}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=March 2020}}\n{{Infobox football biography\