ue released as a promotional eBook in September 2000.\n}}\n{{Book list\n | book_number   = 10\n | title         = [[Crossroads of Twilight]]\n | publish_date  = 7 January 2003\n | aux1          = 822pp (PB) / 681pp (HB)<br />271,632 words\n | aux2          = 26h 03m\n | aux3          = Prologue released as a promotional eBook on July 17, 2002.\n}}\n{{Book list\n | book_number   = 11\n | title         = [[Knife of Dreams]]\n | publish_date  = 11 October 2005\n | aux1          = 837pp (PB) / 761pp (HB)<br />315,163 words\n | aux2          = 32h 24m\n | aux3          = Prologue released as a promotional eBook on July 22, 2005.\n}}\n{{Book list\n | book_number   = 12\n | title         = [[The Gathering Storm (novel)|The Gathering Storm]]\n | publish_date  = 27 October 2009\n | aux1          = 766pp (PB) / 766pp (HB)<br />297,502  words\n | aux2          = 33h 02m\n | aux3          = Completed by Brandon Sanderson.\n}}\n{{Book list\n | book_number   = 13\n | title         = [[Towers of Midnight]]\n | publish_date  = 2 November 2010\n | aux1          = 864pp (PB) / 843pp (HB)<br />327,052 words\n | aux2          = 38h 17m\n | aux3          = Completed by Brandon Sanderson.<ref name=\"Brandon Sanderson's Facebook page\">{{cite web|url=http://www.facebook.com/BrandonSandrson?v=wall&story_fbid=137045153003317|title=Brandon Sanderson's Facebook page}} {{registration required}}</ref>\n}}\n{{Book list\n | book_number   = 14\n | title         = [[A Memory of Light]]\n | publish_date  = 8 January 2013\n | aux1          = 912pp (PB) / 909pp (HB)<br />353,906 words\n | aux2          = 41h 55m\n | aux3          = Completed by [[Brandon Sanderson]],<ref name=\"Brandon Sanderson's Google+ Post\">{{cite web |url= https://plus.google.com/u/0/112625949782182655505/posts/Y5jVWa24AfB |title=Brandon Sanderson \u2013 Google+ \u2013 Today I got up, and I did not have a Wheel of Time book to work on. |first=Brandon |last=Sanderson |authorlink=Brandon Sanderson |date=August 1, 2012 |accessdate=